                            <h4>Online classes</h4>
                            <img src="images/library.jpg" class="img-responsive img-thumbnail">
                            <p class="list-group-item-text col-lg-7 col-md-7 col-sm-7 col-xs-12">
                            After a few days of anxiety, the staff rose to the occasion by chartering a plan of action. They had opted for the Microsoft A3 programme a few months earlier, thus, they began their training. They were trained to conduct online classes during the non-existent ‘Summer holidays’. After many experimentations and a few setbacks, the teachers were finally ready to take on the challenge of virtual classes. It has been a unique year, having to deal with long distance learning and online exams, but the teachers coped really well with the changing circumstances and made it through. As we begin another academic year, we pray everything goes as well as it went last year and that we may be able to go back to physical classes soon.</p>
